It would be good to be able to copy or move a template from one space to another. I believe that Confluence does not currently support this functionality?

 
{panel:title=Atlassian Update - 27 June 2019|borderStyle=solid|borderColor=#ebf2f9|titleBGColor=#ebf2f9|bgColor=#ffffff}
Thanks for voting and commenting on this issue. Your input in the comments helps us understand how this affects you and what you're hoping to accomplish with Confluence. We agree, having the ability to copy templates is something that is useful.

This is something we would like to implement, but this suggestion is not on the Confluence roadmap at the moment. Please remember that jira.atlassian.com is one of many inputs for our roadmap. We will update this issue as we make further progress on it. 
{panel}

