User Management: OSUser / Atlassian User
User Repositories: Internal / JIRA / LDAP (multiple selection possible)

{panel:bgColor=#e7f4fa}
  *NOTE:* This suggestion is for *Confluence Cloud*. Using *Confluence Server*? [See the corresponding suggestion|http://jira.atlassian.com/browse/CONFSERVER-7719].
