It would be really great if Confluence would allow you to send multiple daily update emails, and select the times at which they are sent.  This would not need to be a user customizeable feature, just an admin option set for anyone choosing to subscribe to the daily update email.  For instance, it would be fantastic if I could det confluence to send the daily update emails at 8am and 8pm.  

In fact just being able to tell confluence to send the update emails ever X hours (instead of every 24) would be just as helpful.

