h2. News the last 7 days
\{blog-posts:15|spaces=@all|time=7d|content=excerpts\} 
h3. News the last month
\{blog-posts:15|spaces=@all|starttime=7d|time=30d|content=excerpts\} 

Or a different method for displaying the most recent blog posts bigger7larger than the older ones, and a way of specifying what is recent and older.

